OL,3,CGivan insists he followed the law in
OL,4,Crefusing integrated status for two
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FStormont's Education Minister Paul
OL,8,FGivan has insisted that he followed
OL,9,Fthe law when making a decision to
OL,10,Frefuse applications from two Co Down
OL,11,Fschools for integrated status.
OL,13,FDuring a stormy debate at the Northern
OL,14,FIreland Assembly, the minister's
OL,15,Fdecision was attacked by a series of
OL,16,FAlliance Party MLAs, while opposition
OL,17,Fleader Matthew O'Toole said he
OL,18,Fappeared to have a "vendetta" against
OL,19,Fintegrated education.
