OL,3,CGivan insists he followed the law in
OL,4,Crefusing integrated status for two
OL,5,Cschools
OL,7,FThe two schools, Bangor Academy and
OL,8,FRathmore Primary School, had applied
OL,9,Ffor controlled integrated status from
OL,10,FSeptember 2025 but were both turned
OL,11,Fdown in decisions made on January 7,
OL,12,Fdespite a majority of parents who had
OL,13,Fresponded to a ballot being in favour
OL,14,Fof the change.
OL,16,FThe Education Minister answered an
OL,17,Furgent question on the issue on Monday
OL,18,Fabout how his decision is in line with
OL,19,Fhis duty to support the integrated
OL,20,Fsector.
